show.description: Anjali, a resilient young lawyer, rebuilds her life after betrayal, making an unconventional choice to become a mother on her own. Amid shifting dynamics at her law firm, her guarded boss Rajat finds himself drawn to her strength. As personal and professional lines blur, workplace secrets, emotional awakenings, and unexpected connection forms an unforgettable tale.
